      About this item

      • Smart Kit, Smarter Home: Combine Cync smart devices to create a smarter home in minutes; Wireless smart dimmer switch connects via Bluetooth to the Cync smart light bulb to add lighting touch control anywhere
      • Color Changing Light Bulb: Choose from millions of color options to change the room décor, set schedules, and control the lights from the Cync App, powered by Savant, no hub required
      • Wireless Light Switch: Place the battery-powered dimmer light switch near your front door or closer to your bed without wires or screws; Simply peel off the back and stick your wireless light switch on any wall in your house for smart control; No electrical box needed
      • Easy Control: The Bluetooth dimmer switch adds convenient one-touch control while voice control with Google Home and Amazon Alexa devices (sold separately) allows you to control your WiFi light bulb even when you’re away from home
      • How To Use: Group the wireless switch with other Cync smart switches, smart bulbs or smart plugs in the Cync App for simple control over kitchen lights, the space heater and much more from the bed or couch

      Product Description

      This kit comes with a smart LED light bulb and a wireless light dimmer switch that make it easy to enhance your room light or to celebrate the holidays. Use millions of colors to create the perfect party vibe or support your team on game day with each Cync light bulb. Pair the wire-free smart switch in the Cync App, powered by Savant, to any Cync smart light bulb to dim and brighten the room, creating the perfect dinner time or movie night scene. Add a battery-operated smart switch closer to your bed, front door or wherever you need one for convenient one-touch control anywhere. Get additional confidence by scheduling your Cync lights in the Cync app to turn on so that you improve home security and never come home to a dark house. Use voice control by pairing your Cync Smart LED Light Bulb with Amazon Alexa or Google Assistant (sold separately). Remotely control in the Cync app your WiFi bulb or wireless switch while you’re away on vacation or when your hands are full. Make controlling your colored light bulbs from anywhere in your home a breeze by grouping the wire-free light switch with the smart bulbs in the Cync app.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
